    <item>
      <title>中国监管机构扰乱市场，腾讯回购创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/tencent-buybacks-hit-record-as-china-watchdog-roiled-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[腾讯控股有限公司去年 12 月回购了创纪录的 100 亿港元（13 亿美元）股票，并在 2024 年进一步加快了回购步伐，此前中国游戏监管机构出台的一系列新规定令投资者感到惊讶，引发了广泛的科技股抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/tencent-buybacks-hit-record-as-china-watchdog-roiled-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的复杂信息让投资者对中国保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/xi-s-mixed-messages-leave-whiplashed-investors-wary-of-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，习近平主席一直在努力吸引外资，同时继续重塑中国的营商环境，以确保他的权力在国内外都不会受到挑战。这些有时相互冲突的目标让投资者感到困惑，也让官僚们感到紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/xi-s-mixed-messages-leave-whiplashed-investors-wary-of-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
